OL,3,CThe 'quiet' hospital ward helping new
OL,4,Cmums and babies get home faster
OL,6,FA new mobile app to reduce noise on a
OL,7,Fmother and baby ward at the Royal
OL,8,FCornwall Hospital by diverting noisy
OL,9,Fbedside call-bells is being hailed a
OL,10,Fbig success.
OL,12,FMidwives on the Wheal Fortune Ward
OL,13,Fhave been trialling the new 'Silent
OL,14,FHospital' system.
OL,16,FIt means patients can alert medical
OL,17,Fstaff using an app, instead of ringing
OL,18,Fa noisy buzzer.
