OL,3,CThe 'quiet' hospital ward helping new
OL,4,Cmums and babies get home faster
OL,6,FThe staff say the digital upgrade is
OL,7,Fmaking their lives less stressful
OL,8,Fwhile patients are reporting a much
OL,9,Fcalmer environment. The new setup is
OL,10,Falso leading to patients being
OL,11,Fdischarged an average of half a day
OL,12,Fsooner.
OL,14,FAshley Tindale recently had her fourth
OL,15,Fchild Sorren on the ward. She said it
OL,16,Fwas "very different" compared to her
OL,17,Fexperience with her first baby.
OL,19,F"(There were) lots of bells ringing,
OL,20,Flots of coming and going, whereas this
OL,21,Ftime you didn't have any of that.
