OL,3,CThe 'quiet' hospital ward helping new
OL,4,Cmums and babies get home faster
OL,6,F"I felt like they were lot quicker to
OL,7,Fkind of respond then last time."
OL,9,FThe staff at Wheal Fortune care for
OL,10,Fmums and babies who need extra support
OL,11,Fafter birth and Ashley says it really
OL,12,Fhelped her rest.
OL,14,F"I think that if you've been poorly,
OL,15,Fyou do feel that you're on the back
OL,16,Ffoot so anything that can happen that
OL,17,Fmakes you feel a bit more rested is
OL,18,Freally brilliant," she told ITV News.
OL,20,F"It really did help us. Even my
OL,21,Fhusband commented on it."
