OL,3,CThe 'quiet' hospital ward helping new
OL,4,Cmums and babies get home faster
OL,6,F"It vibrates and gives you three
OL,7,Fsounds as well, but only to the person
OL,8,Fthat the call was going to. So the
OL,9,Fother handsets will remain silent,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,F"The important thing with that is if
OL,13,Fyou're not free, it can move around to
OL,14,Fsomeone that is so the call bell isn't
OL,15,Flost."
OL,17,FThe pilot scheme has been extended to
OL,18,Fthe end of 2025 with more ways of
OL,19,Fsilencing the wards being explored.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
