OL,3,CThe 'quiet' hospital ward helping new
OL,4,Cmums and babies get home faster
OL,6,FRoberta Fuller is programme director
OL,7,Ffor the planned new Women and
OL,8,FChildrens Hospital and says this is
OL,9,Fpart of the modernising the maternity
OL,10,Fwards can do before the hospital is
OL,11,Fbuilt.
OL,13,F"This is the first step into making a
OL,14,Fbetter, more therapeutic environment.
OL,15,FSo we silence call-bells, we can then
OL,16,Fsilence medical equipment, we move on
OL,17,Fto looking at continuous patient
OL,18,Fmonitoring to allow the workforce to
OL,19,Fbe used differently."
